<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Residence" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Residence,</orth> 1) act of dwelling in a place: <emph>out of it</emph> (my displeasure) <cit><quote>you'll run again, rather than suffer question for your r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.5.42" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 5, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>how chances it they travel? their r. was better,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.343" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 343</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) dwelling, habitation: <bibl n="shak. mm 5.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 2.284" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 284</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 2.1.119" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 II, 1, 119</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. II, 3, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.1.97" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 1, 97</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.4.151" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 4, 151</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>